{"tid":1764283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post] 全體社會一同孤立，唾棄，清算黑警!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-12-01T04:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T05:17:13.000Z","uid":120847,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6459e045519b45aadcd2c81dd7dcb3ff11ff9d33","tid":1764283,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:08:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">經過今次運動，香港警察已經徹底腐化，演變成一個與民為敵，嗜血成性，視人命如草芥，視萬物皆螻蟻嘅恐怖集團</span></span><br />\n<br />\n721完全無視市民性命安危<br />\n平日以殘害無辜市民為樂，暴力成癮<br />\n完全泯滅人性<br />\n甚至試圖奪權建立軍政府<br />\n呢個與民為敵嘅武裝組織，任何一個有血性嘅人都唔可以忘記佢地嘅所作所為<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地一定要讓仇恨延續下去，<br />\n直至佢地被清算，被唾棄，被毀滅。</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地要令每一個警員都被社會摒棄同孤立<br />\n作為社會一員，你有責任<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1.做生意/開舖嘅你，今日起因行政同保安理由，拒絕服務警員，並張貼呢張平安符係門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可保生意興隆，貨如輪轉<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/LgZJF7p.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 打工嘅你，迫於無奈要為黑警提供服務時，可以調節一下服務態度質素同效率<br />\n<br />\n3. 有朋友親戚做黑警嘅話，以最惡毒說話咀咒佢同佢地全家，然後同佢立即斷絕來往，並鼓勵其他朋友一同孤立黑警<br />\n<br />\n4. 有小朋友/為人師表嘅你，向小朋友講解黑警嘅暴行，教導佢地明辨是非，並且提防黑警保護自己<br />\n<br />\n5. 一同向各國政府要求制裁香港警察<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然大家武力不對等，我地就無謂再送頭<br />\n我地以社會壓力將呢群禽獸孤立起黎<br />\n呢個係作為一個人應有嘅基本良知同底線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NrSSWn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NrSSWn.png&h=e8610c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6voZAe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6voZAe.jpg&h=6ee10906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLasGOA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLasGOA.png&h=d0d7bf15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEAgz8B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEAgz8B.jpg&h=878bcd50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CHUk1OZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCHUk1OZ.jpg&h=1a39d28a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CWxe6fF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCWxe6fF.jpg&h=ba3c5b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RyxiYiQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRyxiYiQ.jpg&h=8b28fb16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E5oJ9qu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE5oJ9qu.jpg&h=735d20fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qP4huqw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqP4huqw.png&h=fadca241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w20P4YS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw20P4YS.jpg&h=b5ee3f53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0tMvPqU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0tMvPqU.png&h=02e96cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗恥，猶未雪；<br />\n太子恨，何時滅。<br />\n駕長車踏破軍器廠街。<br />\n壯志饑餐黑警肉，笑談渴飲衙差血。<br />\n待從頭，收拾舊山河，朝天闕。</span></span>"},{"pid":"dbf036d0977c1e37ec9e1cd6994d828fd06402d0","tid":1764283,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ad4a5497e08be6754a09949cfda1625a5d0e43","tid":1764283,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.